```plantuml
@startuml elpapi42_deep-deblurring

!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<Frontend>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<Backend>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<ModelServing>> LightYellow
  BackgroundColor<<Storage>> LightGray
}

component "Vue.js Frontend" <<Frontend>> as Frontend
component "Flask Backend" <<Backend>> as Backend
component "TensorFlow Serving" <<ModelServing>> as ModelServing
component "Cloudinary" <<Storage>> as Cloudinary
component "Redis" <<Storage>> as Redis
component "PostgreSQL" <<Storage>> as PostgreSQL
component "Model Repository" as ModelRepo

Frontend -down-> Backend : HTTP/REST
Backend -down-> ModelServing : gRPC
Backend -down-> Cloudinary : API
Backend -down-> Redis : Cache/Sessions
Backend -down-> PostgreSQL : Data Storage
ModelServing -right-> ModelRepo : Load Model

note right of Frontend
  User interface for
  image deblurring
end note

note right of Backend
  API Gateway
  Orchestrates communication
end note

note right of ModelServing
  Exposes DeblurGAN-V2
  for inference
end note

note right of ModelRepo
  Stores trained model
  and training scripts
end note

@enduml
```